What is gtksurf?
----------------

gtksurf is graphical frontend to surf, the visualization tool for real
algebraic geometry.

Visit surf's homepage for more information:

		      http://surf.sourceforge.net


Basic Installation:
-------------------

As usual:

./configure
make
(become root)
make install


